title: The Swap 2
overview: Beautiful superstar, Lene Hefner, is married to Jon Dough. Leena and Marc are also married, but Leena and Jon have something in common: They're both swingers at heart, but not at home. Paul Thomas takes Lene and Leena and teams them up with the cast list of the year - Christina Angel, Dyanna Lauren, Asia Carrera, Misty Rain and Isis Nile included - to revisit a subject he has explored repeatedly, professionally only, of course. "The Swap 2": Is it about you?
